    "statement": "---\nFor support please use the [Google group forum](http://groups.google.com/group/robotics-tool-box?hl=en) rather than GitHub issues.  There are more people participating and you'll likely get a quicker response.  Checkout the [FAQ](https://petercorke.com/toolboxes/faq) before you post a question, it covers common problems that arise with incorrect MATLAB paths.",
